<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: #000000 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: #000000 10px solid" width="50%">
<p><font color="#1874cd"><strong><span style="COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"> </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><font size="+0"><span style="COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"> 신규 사막맵 &#8216;미라마&#8217; 공개</span></font></span></strong></font></p>
</td>
